  {g:"INFRASTRUCTURE",items:[{id:"hsm",icon:"🛡",label:"HSM / Primus"},{id:"qkd",icon:"⚛",label:"QKD Interface"},{id:"mpc",icon:"🧩",label:"MPC Engine"},{id:"cluster",icon:"☁",label:"Cluster"}]},
  {g:"GOVERNANCE",items:[{id:"approvals",icon:"✅",label:"Approvals"},{id:"alerts",icon:"🔔",label:"Alert Center"},{id:"audit",icon:"📝",label:"Audit Log"},{id:"compliance",icon:"📋",label:"Compliance"},{id:"sbom",icon:"📊",label:"SBOM / CBOM"}]},
